# Ansible templates and Config file manipulation

## One of the tasks that Ansible is used for is application installation and provisioning (i.e. config file manipulation)

### Known pattern for this kind of tasks is using Jinja2 template files with {{ variable }} that is replaced during ansible playbook execution with either Environment variables of Ansible facts

### put your config template file (vim.j2) into 
/template/ directory

more details are in:
https://www.redhat.com/sysadmin/ansible-templates-configuration

<tba> how to create j2 template file from Terraform output
